Great movie.  Partway through my English subtitles hung-up for a few minutes but I don't know if that is because of my DVD player on my computer.  I'll try playing this again on a different platform and update my review.

I love it A great movie for the entire family, the special effects are great and the colors are crisp and clean. A movie for those who play Tennis as well for those who do not participate in this sport.
